    "source_text": "Asthma is the most common chronic respiratory inflammatory disease in childhood.As long as we grasp the indications of acute and chronic treatment and referral，primary medical and health institutions should be the best platform for asthma prevention and treatment.This suggestions refers to the recent domestic and foreign relevant industry standards，research data and management guidelines，and publishes more specific understanding and interpretation of clinical diagnosis and treatment strategies for children's bronchial asthma，and puts forward more operational requirements and programs for clinical practice.This suggestions is divided into seven parts：early screening of children's asthma，detection of children's asthma pulmonary function，recognition of children's allergic symptoms and detection of allergens，assessment tool of asthma control based on grass-roots hospital，treatment strategy of children's asthma in grass-roots hospital，recommended scheme of children's asthma maintenance period treatment and two-way referral standard and process.Based on the treatment goal of children's asthma，the whole process of diagnosis and treatment is improved combing，focusing on the 'key points'，especially according to the 'treatment time axis' to develop the corresponding treatment plan，can maximize the standardization and normalization of management，in order to provide a reference for the chronic disease management in primary medical and health institutions."
